query:
SELECT
                id                          AS "id!",
                user_id                     AS "user_id!: Uuid",
                created_at                  AS "created_at!",
                last_used_at                AS "last_used_at?",
                revoked_at                  AS "revoked_at?",
                refresh_token_id           AS "refresh_token_id?",
                refresh_token_issued_at     AS "refresh_token_issued_at?"
            FROM auth_sessions
            WHERE id = $1
